msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/complete"
msgid ""
"Congratulations, you have finished the third tutorial (AT guns and "
"artillery)."
msgstr ""
"Enhorabuena, has terminado el tercer tutorial (cañones AT y artillería)."

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/date"
msgid "June 24th, 1941 · Border with the USSR"
msgstr "24 de junio de 1941 - Frontera con la URSS"

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/hint_video"
msgid "Press this button to re-watch the video for this tutorial phase."
msgstr "Pulsa este botón para volver a ver el vídeo de esta fase del tutorial."

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/name"
msgid "Tutorial 3: AT Guns and Artillery"
msgstr "Tutorial 3: Cañones AT y Artillería"

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/name_big"
msgid "AT Guns and Artillery"
msgstr "Cañones AT y Artillería"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/narrator/"
"ger_officer/00"
msgid ""
"Soldaten! Welcome back to the front line! Today you will learn how to deploy "
"Anti-Tank guns, build sandbags, and distinguish between direct and indirect "
"fire units."
msgstr ""
"¡Soldados! ¡Bienvenido de nuevo al frente! Hoy aprenderás a desplegar "
"cañones antitanque (AT), a construir sacos de arena y a distinguir entre "
"unidades de fuego directo e indirecto."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/narrator/"
"ger_officer/01"
msgid "First, use all of your soldiers to crew the Anti-Tank gun."
msgstr ""
"Primero, quiero que todos os metais a tripular el cañón antitanque (AT)."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/narrator/"
"ger_officer/01b"
msgid ""
"Soldiers, it's time to relocate the AT gun to a new firing position near the "
"pond. Move it!"
msgstr ""
"Soldados, es hora de trasladar el cañón AT a una nueva posición de disparo "
"cerca de la laguna. ¡Movéos!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/narrator/"
"ger_officer/02"
msgid ""
"Great! Now it's time to build sandbags around your AT gun for extra "
"protection!"
msgstr ""
"¡Estupendo! ¡Ahora es el momento de construir sacos de arena alrededor de tu "
"cañón AT para una mayor protección!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/narrator/"
"ger_officer/03"
msgid "Enemy vehicles down the road! Wipe them out!"
msgstr "¡Vehículos enemigos por la carretera! ¡Acaba con ellos!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/narrator/"
"ger_officer/04"
msgid ""
"What is this?! It's a heavy Soviet tank, a KV-1! Take it out immediately "
"using APCR rounds!"
msgstr ""
"¿Qué es ese monstruo? ¡Es un tanque pesado, un KV-1! ¡Acaba con él "
"utilizando proyectiles de alta velocidad APCR!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/narrator/"
"ger_officer/04b"
msgid ""
"Great job destroying the heavy tank! Now let us prepare to relocate again."
msgstr ""
"¡Buen trabajo destruyendo el tanque pesado! Ahora preparémonos para "
"reubicarnos de nuevo."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/narrator/"
"ger_officer/05"
msgid ""
"Here, take this truck and attach your AT gun to it so you can tow it quickly "
"to a new location."
msgstr ""
"Toma, coge este camión y remolca tu cañón AT para poder re-ubicarlo "
"rápidamente a una nueva posición."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/narrator/"
"ger_officer/05b"
msgid "Detach the AT gun and move it into position near the trenches!"
msgstr "Desacopla el cañón AT y poiciónalo cerca de las trincheras"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/narrator/"
"ger_officer/06a"
msgid ""
"Now we will familiarize ourselves with our standard light field howitzer, "
"the 10.5cm LeFH 18! First, you need some ammunition for it."
msgstr ""
"Ahora nos familiarizaremos con nuestro obús de campaña estándar, ¡el LeFH 18 "
"de 10,5 cm! En primer lugar, necesitas munición para él."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/narrator/"
"ger_officer/06b"
msgid ""
"You now possess an ammunition truck. Crew the artillery piece and drive the "
"truck closer to resupply your howitzer!"
msgstr ""
"Ahora ya tienes un camión de municiones. ¡Ponéos a tripular el obús y "
"acercad el camión para reabastecerlo!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/narrator/"
"ger_officer/07"
msgid ""
"Soviets have arrived at the village west of our location. Use the howitzer "
"to destroy their trucks!"
msgstr ""
"Los soviéticos han llegado a la aldea situada al oeste de nuestra posición. "
"¡Utiliza el obús para destruir sus camiones!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/narrator/"
"ger_officer/07helper"
msgid ""
"Firing multiple shots at the same target or location increases the accuracy "
"of each subsequent shot."
msgstr ""
"Disparar varias veces al mismo blanco o lugar aumenta la precisión de cada "
"disparo posterior."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/narrator/"
"ger_officer/08"
msgid ""
"Soviets armored car spotted! Switch the howitzer ammunition to either armor-"
"piercing (APHE) or high-explosive anti-tank (HEAT) to destroy it with direct "
"fire!"
msgstr ""
"¡Vehículo blindado soviético avistado! ¡Cambia la munición del obús a "
"perforante (APHE) o antitanque de alto explosivo (HEAT) para destruirlo con "
"fuego directo!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/narrator/"
"ger_officer/09"
msgid "An exceptional kill! Now, kill the remaining enemy soldiers!"
msgstr "¡Un tiro excepcional! Ahora, ¡Acaba con los demás soldados enemigos!"

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/hint/01"
msgid ""
"Your AT gun is set to 'return fire' firing mode. Switch to 'fire at will' or "
"manually shoot in direct control mode."
msgstr ""
"Tu cañón AT está configurado en modo de disparo de 'fuego de retorno'. "
"Cambia a 'fuego a discreción' o dispara manualmente en modo de control "
"directo."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/narrator/scene/01"
msgid ""
"This is the 5cm PaK 38. It is a direct-fire Anti-Tank weapon. Ideal for "
"ambushing enemy tanks with pinpoint accuracy."
msgstr ""
"Éste es el PaK 38 de 5 cm. Es un arma antitanque de fuego directo. Ideal "
"para tender emboscadas a los tanques enemigos con una precisión milimétrica."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/narrator/scene/02"
msgid ""
"Changing your location is always good idea. For example, your new location "
"should allow for an even better angle of the road."
msgstr ""
"Cambiar de ubicación siempre es una buena idea. Por ejemplo, tu nueva "
"ubicación te dará aún mejores vistas a la carretera."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/narrator/scene/03"
msgid "Tow your AT gun to the new position using the truck."
msgstr "Remolca tu cañón AT hasta la nueva posición utilizando el camión."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/outro_completed"
msgid ""
"Mission Accomplished!\n"
"\n"
"Click on 'continue' to keep playing this mission or click on 'next' to "
"proceed directly into the next mission."
msgstr ""
"¡Misión cumplida!\n"
"\n"
"Haz clic en \"Continuar\" para seguir jugando esta misión o en \"Siguiente\" "
"para pasar directamente a la siguiente misión."

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/place"
msgid "Army Group Centre"
msgstr "Grupo de Ejércitos Centro"

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/reinf_video"
msgid "Re-watch steps."
msgstr "Repetir el video"

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/replay_video"
msgid "Replay Video"
msgstr "Repetir el video"

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/story"
msgid ""
"Welcome to artillery training, Soldier.\n"
"\n"
"In this tutorial you will learn the basics of artillery emplacements and how "
"their direct and indirect fire modes can be decisive in battle.\n"
"\n"
"Where artillery lacks in mobility, it makes up for in firepower.\n"
"\n"
"                                        Good luck!"
msgstr ""
"Bienvenido al entrenamiento de artillería, soldado.\n"
"\n"
"En este tutorial aprenderás los fundamentos de los emplazamientos de "
"artillería y cómo sus modos de fuego directo e indirecto pueden ser "
"decisivos en la batalla.\n"
"\n"
"A pesar de que la artillería carece de movilidad, lo compensa con su "
"potencia de fuego.\n"
"\n"
"                                        ¡Que tengas suerte!"

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/task1"
msgid "Crew the AT gun with all your men."
msgstr "Tripula el cañón AT con todos tus hombres."

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/task1b"
msgid "Move your AT gun to a new location as shown."
msgstr "Mueve tu cañón AT a una nueva ubicación como se muestra."

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/task2"
msgid "Build sandbags for your AT gun."
msgstr "Construye sacos de arena para tu cañón AT."

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/task3"
msgid "Destroy the enemy vehicles!"
msgstr "¡Destruye los vehículos enemigos!"

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/task4"
msgid "Destroy the enemy KV-1!"
msgstr "¡Destruye el KV-1 enemigo!"

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/task5a"
msgid "Connect your AT gun to the truck for towing."
msgstr "Remolca el cañón AT con el camión"

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/task5"
msgid "Tow the AT gun to the new position as indicated."
msgstr "Lleva el cañón AT hasta la nueva posición, como se indica."

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/task5b"
msgid "Detach the AT gun and move it into the given position."
msgstr "Desengancha el arma AT y colócala en la posición indicada."

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/task6"
msgid "Resupply the light field howitzer."
msgstr "Reabastece el obús."

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/task7"
msgid "Destroy the enemy trucks with the howitzer."
msgstr "Destruye los camiones enemigos con el obús."

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/task8"
msgid "Destroy the Soviet armored car with direct fire with AP/HEAT shells."
msgstr ""
"Destruye el blindado soviético con fuego directo con proyectiles antitanque "
"APHE o HEAT."

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/task9"
msgid "Destroy the remaining enemy units."
msgstr "Destruye las unidades enemigas restantes."

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/outro_failed"
msgid "You have been defeated!"
msgstr "¡Has sido derrotado!"
